  "title": "BIM Modeller & Draughtsman",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Develop detailed 3D models of building projects using BIM software.</li>\n  <li>Create accurate 2D drawings and construction details in line with Singapore's regulations.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with project stakeholders to integrate their designs into the BIM models.</li>\n  <li>Identify and resolve clashes between different building systems.</li>\n  <li>Update and maintain BIM models throughout the project.</li>\n  <li>Extract quantity information for cost estimation and construction planning.</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with Singapore's building regulations and standards.</li>\n  <li>Perform quality checks on BIM deliverables.</li>\n  <li>Handle materials submission, ensuring accuracy and adherence to specifications.</li>\n  <li>Manage project administration, including support for tender submissions, quotations, purchasing, and inventory management.</li>\n  <li>Support the work done claim process with relevant documentation and drawings.</li>\n  <li>Provide training and support to team members on BIM software.</li>\n  <li>Attend site meetings as needed.</li>\n  <li>Perform administrative tasks to ensure the office runs smoothly and fosters a positive work environment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proficiency in BIM software, especially Autodesk Revit.</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with Singapore's BIM practices and workflows.</li>\n  <li>Strong drafting skills with attention to detail.</li>\n  <li>Ability to interpret 2D drawings and create accurate 3D models.</li>\n  <li>Effective communication and collaboration skills.</li>\n  <li>Problem-solving abilities for clash detection and resolution.</li>\n  <li>Time management skills to meet project deadlines.</li>\n  <li>A relevant diploma or degree in architecture, engineering, or drafting is preferred.</li>\n  <li>Previous experience in BIM modeling or drafting in the Singapore construction industry is a plus.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Please apply via <strong>MyCareerFuture</strong> or <strong>email</strong><em> </em>your updated CV to <strong>recruit@wsg.com.sg</strong>.</p>",
